      "content": "sometimes i sit here in this apartment and it hits me that if i just stopped existing tomorrow, the world wouldn't even flinch. like, i'm just a ghost in this city. nobody knows me, and honestly, i don't think anyone would even notice the gap i left behind. it’s like i’m just taking up space that doesn't belong to me.",
